The 13 things are:
1. Dark matter and Dark energy
2. http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pioneer_Anomaly
3. Varying Constants
4. Cold Fusion
5. Origin of life
6. Life on Mars?
7. http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wow!_Signal
8. Large viruses
9. Aging and death
10. Evolution of sexual reproduction
11. Free will
12. Placebo effect
13. Homeopathy

Might not make any sense to you, but it makes perfect sense to the homeless guy living in an alley nearby:

IT'S ALL DAMN FUCKED UP.
